# 'X11 error: BadAlloc (insufficient resources for operation)'

Workaround: not use '-vo xv'

# Play DVD in folder

```
mplayer -dvd-device /path/to/dvd/folder dvd://
```

# 3d

using stereo3d filter

```bash
mplayer2 -vf stereo3d,scale 1.mkv
mplayer2 -vf stereo3d=sbs2l,scale 1.mkv #Half-width side-by-side 
```

